metadata.description: Moonlit Rooftop" portrays a tranquil scene on a city rooftop. A girl sits serenely amidst a vibrant sky adorned with glimmering stars and a crescent moon. With its cozy, lo-fi anime style, the artwork invites viewers to immerse themselves in the peaceful ambiance of this rooftop sanctuary within a bustling skyscraper city.
metadata.name: Moonlit Rooftop #1/10
